<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="6Sep1938"><font color="red">6 September 1938</font> <i>MERC</i> (Jacques Mercanton memoir): back at the hotel he found pages of MS inviting him to more work, clippings of articles about Dublin, letters, a resum&eacute; in English of Zimmer&apos;s book on Finn MacCool &ldquo;a great shadow&rdquo; and the pocket notebook in which he made entries while I read aloud </div>
